# Shared defaults. CLI flags still win over everything in this file, and
# shell/CI env wins over both base and namespace sections.
# Your platform operator provides all three values; the CLI has no built-in
# control endpoint.
CONTROL_URL=https://<your-control-plane>
WDL_NS=<your-namespace>
ADMIN_TOKEN=<your-tenant-token>

# Add a [<ns>] section only when you need to override any of the base values
# (e.g. a different token or control plane for a uat namespace).
#
# [uat]
# CONTROL_URL=https://api.uat.example.com
# ADMIN_TOKEN=<uat-ns-token>
